/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*\

Class
    Foam::RSTEauxiliaryFunctions

Description
    Auxiliary functions for the Reynolds stress transport equation (RSTE)
    budget library, providing reusable building blocks for budget term evaluation.

Functions included
    - Pressure diffusion (velocityâ€“pressure products, D_p,ij)
    - Turbulent transport (triple velocity products)
    - Dissipation (products of velocity gradients)

SourceFile
    RSTEauxiliaryFunctions.C

Authors
    2025  Christoffer Hansen & Mario Javier Rincon

\*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

//--------------------------------------------------------------------------------//
// Functions for the Pressure Diffusion D_p,ij
//--------------------------------------------------------------------------------//

Up
{
    type            multiply;
    libs            ("libfieldFunctionObjects.so");
    fields          (U p);
    enabled         true;
    log             false;
    result          Up;
    executeControl  timeStep;
    executeInterval 1;
    writeControl    none;              
}

